        Product Description

        Nynicorny language translator pen adopts OCR scanning technology and the accuracy is as high as 99%.Whether you are a tourist,lawyer, professor, administrator,student or salesperson,this Pen Scanner Translator will improve your workflow efficiency.

        A perfect gift for children, students and your friends and family.

        • Supporting Online Translation in 112 Languages: Arabic, Polish, Danish, German, Russian, French, Finnish, Korean, Dutch, Czech, Romanian, Portuguese, Swedish, Japanese, Thai, Turkish, Spanish, Greek, Hungarian, Italian, English, Hindi, Indonesian, Vietnamese, Cantonese, Chinese, Kurdish, Persian, Slovak, Bulgarian, Hebrew, Malay, Norwegian, Croatian ,Khmer etc.
        • 12 Language Offline Translations: Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, English, Japanese, Korean, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, German, Italian, Cantonese
        • Text excerpts (21 languages offline): Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, English American, German, Spanish, French, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Dutch, Portuguese, Russian, Czech, Danish, Finnish, Greek, Hungarian, Norwegian, Polish, Swedish, Turkish

        • System Languages (12): Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, English, Japanese, Korean, French ,Spanish, Vietnamese, Russian, German, Italian,Thai.
        • Scan Online and Offline (12 languages): SimplifiedChinese,traditionalChinese,English,Japanese,Korean,French,Spanish,Portuguese,Russian,German,Italian,Cantonese.
        • Photo Translation (11 languages): Simplified Chinese,traditional Chinese,English,Japanese,Korean,French,Spanish,Portuguese,Russian,German,Italian

        HD Camera

        Pen scanner with 5 million pixel high-definition can scan 3000 characters per minute, quickly scan a whole line of text and translate instantly.Translation pen scanner up to 99% accurate recognition rate.

        Bluetooth 4.0

        Bluetooth 4.0 can connect to Bluetooth headsets and speakers easily. Stable signal and fast connection.Easy to use, bringing an immersive translation experience.

        Long Battery Life

        High-capacity,super-large capacity and long battery life.Scanning without concern of low battery.It satisfies the translation time to a large extent without worrying about power failure.

        Supporting offline translation and using alone.

        Achieves 99% accuracy

        3-inch HD touch screen, real-time voice and text display.

        Support photo translation.

        Two-way Instant Translator

        32G large capacity, the background is updated from time to time.

        Intelligent noise reduction recognition.

            How customer reviews and ratings work

            Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

            To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
